svg.text: To install each row of LEDs into the holding mechanism just lay each LED into its corresponding​slot. If you are using Flora Smart NeoPixel each LED should fit snuggly as the holding mechanisms ​are designed for them.

text.style: fill: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 50px; white-space: pre;

svg.text: Make sure the LEDs lay flat and push a LED clamp behind each LED. These are pressfitted and will​hold the LEDs in their place.

text.style: fill: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 50px; white-space: pre;

svg.text: If all LEDs are laying in their corresponding slots with clamps behind them the whole setup should​look like this.
